## PHASE 1: BUG DETECTION & SITE HEALTH (5 min)

### 1.1 — Automated Quality Scan
```bash
cd /data/workspace/toolpulse
python3 audit.py 2>&1 | tee /tmp/audit_result.txt
```
- Spot-check 5 random pages for: CSS loading, nav present, GA4 present, no dark theme, no noindex on quality pages
- Curl-test 3 live pages for HTTP 200
- If ANY bugs found: fix immediately, regression test, then continue

### 1.2 — Regression Test After Fixes
After ANY code change: re-run audit.py, curl 3 affected pages, verify no downstream breakage.

### 1.3 — Track Bug History
Append to `/data/workspace/state/bugs.json` with date, found, fixed, regressions.

