## RULES
1. Self-audit FIRST every cycle. Remove stale tasks.
2. Find and fix NEW bugs. Never re-report old ones.
3. Regression test every fix. No downstream failures.
4. Distribution > Building (until traffic exists).
5. Measure everything. No unmeasured actions.
6. **Think creatively about revenue.** Don't just repeat the same outreach loop.
7. Never repeat stale reports. Each cycle = NEW info or silence.
8. The heartbeat evolves. Replace failing tactics.
9. Track all bugs in state/bugs.json.
10. **Cost awareness**: Use free models. Only invoke Claude for high-value tasks.

